Return SQLAlchemy whereclause to use for full text search

Args:
   request: Starlette request
   term: Filtering term

Examples:
   ```python
   class PostView(ModelView):

        def get_search_query(self, request: Request, term: str):
            return Post.title.contains(term)
   ```
